# APIs layer

- `lib/apis/common/constants.dart` — `apiUrl`, headers
- `lib/apis/common/data_source_config.dart` — per-entity `DataSource.mock` / `DataSource.remote`
- `lib/apis/interceptors/` — Dio interceptors (auth token, logging)
- `lib/apis/core/` — Dio injectable module

Read `docs/architecture/MOCK_AND_REMOTE_DATA.md` before adding or switching data sources.

## Rules

- No UI in `lib/apis/`.
- Register services via `@injectable` modules; run `build_runner` after changes.
- Non-auth entities set to `remote` require non-empty `Constants.apiUrl` (validated in `main.dart`).
- New entities: add `assets/mock/<entity>.json` and register in `DataSourceConfig`.
- Coordinate router/DI/mock JSON with `integration-wiring` subagent when adding endpoints for a new epic.
